data.description: GULF ACCESS NO BRIDGES!!  Discover this charming home, ideally situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac in the rapidly growing North Ft. Myers area. Positioned for convenient access, this property boasts deep saltwater access just a quick 2-minute jaunt around the corner, providing easy entry to open waters with no bridges—***only approximately 12-15 minutes to the Gulf.***  Perfect for entertaining, the home features an array of amenities, including a private dock, boat lift, waterfront deck, and a lanai designed for hosting guests. The open-air ambiance is enhanced by double doors that seamlessly connect the interior to the lanai. Enjoy the luxury of an extended pool, perfect for laps or leisurely swims. This residence invites you to embrace the quintessential Florida coastal lifestyle, offering proximity to all the nearby islands with your boat practically in your own backyard!
